title: winhttp
extract: Microsoft Windows HTTP Services (WinHTTP) provides developers with a server-supported, high-level interface to the HTTP/1.1 Internet protocol. ... WinINet displays a user interface for some operations such as collecting user credentials.May 30, 2018
